    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_01-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "（見回りの先生もいないし……）\n（昨日買ったねりけし開けちゃおうっと！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（There're no teachers on patrol‚ either…）\n（I should open the Nerikeshi I bought yesterday!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.5333332896,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.3666666229
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_01-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "（あ、でも、ねりけしっておもちゃ？）\n（それとも文房具？　うーん、微妙なとこだなぁ……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Ah‚ by the way‚ is Nerikeshi a toy?）\n（Or a school supply? Ummー‚ it's a subtle part…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.3666666229,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_01-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "（学校におもちゃは持って来ちゃダメ……だよね……）\n（う～、触りたくてうずうずするよ～）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Not allowed to bring toys to… school…）\n（Ooh~‚ I'm itching to touch it~）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.7666666229,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.9000040253
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_01-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "（はっ！　消しゴムとして使うなら文房具、だよね？）\n（それなら学校で使うのもアリ……？　うん、アリだ！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Ha! If it's used as an eraser‚ it's a school supply‚ right?）\n（Then‚ is it possible to use it at school…? Yes‚ it is!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.9000040253,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.9666732351
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_01-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "（解答に間違いさえ見つければ消しゴムとして）\n（ねりけしが使える……！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（If I find a mistake in the answer‚）\n（I can use Nerikesh as an eraser…!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.9666732351,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.0000065684
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
