      "text": "（見直し、見直し……どこかに間違いは……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Check‚ check… there's a mistake somewhere…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.0000065684,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_01-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "（あ、あった！　ここのthatはthisだよね）\n（それに、ここの選択肢もaじゃなくてbの方が自然……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Oh‚ there it is! 'that' here should be 'this'）\n（Also‚ the natural choice here is b‚ not a…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.0000073313,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
