      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_01-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "（うわぁ！　本物のねりけしってこんなに伸びるんだ！）\n（消しカスで自作したのと全然違うっ！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Wow! Real Nerikeshi stretches like this!）\n（It's completely different from the one I made myself using eraser dust!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.2666775583,
      "sfxList": []
